fsrtool.structure: CREATE TABLE `fsrtool_ships_log` ( `Id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `corpID` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `shipID` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `charName` char(32) NOT NULL DEFAULT '', `time` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `timeback` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', PRIMARY KEY (`Id`,`corpID`) ) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8
